---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="About — Yannik Peschke" 
  description="Learn more about Yannik Peschke, software engineer specializing in frontend architecture and distributed systems."
>

<h1>About Me</h1>

<p class="intro">
  Software engineer with a passion for building scalable web applications and sharing knowledge through writing.
</p>

<p>
  I specialize in frontend architecture, with a particular focus on microfrontends and distributed systems. 
  My work involves designing systems that allow multiple teams to work independently while maintaining 
  consistency and performance across the entire application.
</p>

<p>
  Over the years, I've learned that the best architectures aren't the most complex ones, but those that 
  are composable, maintainable, and aligned with how teams actually work. I believe in pragmatic solutions 
  that solve real problems rather than following trends blindly.
</p>

<p>
  When I'm not coding, I enjoy reading technical books, exploring new technologies, and writing about 
  what I've learned. I'm based in Schwäbisch Gmünd, Germany, and I'm always open to interesting 
  conversations about software architecture and engineering practices.
</p>

<h2>Experience & Focus Areas</h2>

<div class="experience-grid">
  <div class="experience-item">
    <div class="experience-header">
      <div class="experience-title">Frontend Architecture</div>
      <div class="experience-period">Current Focus</div>
    </div>
    <p class="experience-description">
      Designing and implementing scalable frontend architectures using microfrontend patterns, 
      module federation, and modern web technologies. Focus on team autonomy, independent deployments, 
      and maintaining consistency across distributed systems.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="experience-item">
    <div class="experience-header">
      <div class="experience-title">System Design</div>
      <div class="experience-period">Core Expertise</div>
    </div>
    <p class="experience-description">
      Creating composable systems that scale with organization growth. Experience with distributed 
      architectures, API design, and building systems that balance complexity with maintainability. 
      Strong focus on identifying the right boundaries and abstractions.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="experience-item">
    <div class="experience-header">
      <div class="experience-title">Technical Writing</div>
      <div class="experience-period">Ongoing</div>
    </div>
    <p class="experience-description">
      Writing in-depth articles about software architecture, microfrontends, and lessons learned 
      from building production systems. Sharing practical insights and patterns that emerge from 
      real-world implementations.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<h2>Core Skills</h2>

<div class="skills-grid">
  <div class="skill-category">
    <h3>Architecture</h3>
    <p class="skill-list">
      Microfrontends, Module Federation, System Design, Distributed Systems, API Design, 
      Domain-Driven Design, Event-Driven Architecture
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="skill-category">
    <h3>Frontend</h3>
    <p class="skill-list">
      TypeScript, React, Web Components, Build Tools (Webpack, Vite), State Management, 
      Performance Optimization, Accessibility
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="skill-category">
    <h3>Backend & Infrastructure</h3>
    <p class="skill-list">
      Node.js, REST APIs, GraphQL, Docker, CI/CD, Testing Strategies, Monitoring & Observability
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="skill-category">
    <h3>Practices</h3>
    <p class="skill-list">
      Technical Writing, Code Review, Mentoring, Agile Methodologies, Documentation, 
      Cross-Team Collaboration
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="contact-section">
  <h2 style="margin-top: 0;">Get in Touch</h2>
  <p>
    I'm always interested in connecting with other engineers, discussing architecture patterns, 
    or exploring collaboration opportunities.
  </p>
  <div class="contact-links">
    <a href="https://github.com/YanPes" class="contact-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>
    <a href="mailto:contact@yannikpeschke.dev" class="contact-link">Email</a>
    <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/yannikpeschke" class="contact-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LinkedIn</a>
  </div>
</div>

</Layout>

<style>
.intro {
  font-size: 1.25rem;
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
}

.experience-grid {
  display: grid;
  gap: var(--spacing-lg);
  margin-top: var(--spacing-md);
}

.experience-item {
  padding-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
}

.experience-item:last-child {
  border-bottom: none;
}

.experience-header {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: flex-start;
  margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: var(--spacing-xs);
}

.experience-title {
  font-family: var(--font-sans);
  font-size: 1.125rem;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--text-primary);
}

.experience-period {
  font-family: var(--font-sans);
  font-size: 14px;
  color: var(--text-tertiary);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
}

.experience-description {
  font-size: 1rem;
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  line-height: 1.6;
}

.skills-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
  gap: var(--spacing-md);
  margin-top: var(--spacing-md);
}

.skill-category {
  padding: var(--spacing-md);
  background-color: var(--bg-secondary);
  border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
}

.skill-category h3 {
  font-family: var(--font-sans);
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 500;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  color: var(--text-tertiary);
  margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
}

.skill-list {
  font-size: 1rem;
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  line-height: 1.8;
}

.contact-section {
  margin-top: var(--spacing-xl);
  padding: var(--spacing-lg);
  background-color: var(--bg-secondary);
  border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
}

.contact-links {
  display: flex;
  gap: var(--spacing-md);
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  margin-top: var(--spacing-md);
}

.contact-link {
  font-family: var(--font-sans);
  color: var(--text-primary);
  text-decoration: none;
  padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
  border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  transition: all 0.2s ease;
}

.contact-link:hover {
  background-color: var(--accent);
  color: var(--bg-primary);
  border-color: var(--accent);
}

h2:first-of-type {
  margin-top: var(--spacing-lg);
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .skills-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }

  .experience-header {
    flex-direction: column;
  }
}
</style>
